title: Obsidian
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee house, bar, and live music venue that's all ages before 9pm. Food is offered all day, brunch on the weekends til 2pm. Vegans could get waffle made with vegan batter, or marinated tempeh in a panini or served with kale and dates. There is also a curried rice with dates, almonds, red pepper, cilantro. Has soy and hemp milk for coffee drinks (at extra charge).
